// In the config (line 75):
nodes: [ImageNode, HeadingNode, QuoteNode, MentionNode],
```

**Also update all read-only LexicalComposer instances in ContentView.jsx:**

At `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\src\components\HomePage\ContentViewer\ContentView.jsx`, there are three `LexicalComposer` instances (lines 407-419 for repost source, line 583-595 for normal post). All must include `MentionNode` in their `nodes` array:

```javascript
